      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="Post an invoice for the asset to the fixed asset sub-ledger to recognize the acquisition of the asset. An integration point exists with accounts payable, which should advise the asset manager that an asset needs to be capitalized.If the asset is acquired via an internal or intercompany acquisition, determine the appropriate price to record the asset in accordance with generally accepted accounting principles."/>
